edu.usm.cos420.antenatal.domain

Class PregnancyFollowUp

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.usm.cos420.antenatal.domain.PregnancyRecord
      • edu.usm.cos420.antenatal.domain.PregnancyFollowUp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IPregnancyRecord

    public class PregnancyFollowUp
extends PregnancyRecord
    The PregnancyFollowUp class represents a follow up visit of the initial visit with the id given. These visits record only a subset of the information from the initial visit, including date, blood pressure, weight, fundal height, blood film, and referred.
